Question/Assignment Description:
Write a program that takes a list of numbers and calculates the sum and average of those numbers. The program should be able to handle any number of inputs and should output both the sum and the average. The inputs will be provided as a list, and you must ensure to handle cases where the list is empty.Skeleton Code:program SumAndAverage

    dictionary
        numbers: list of integer
        sum: integer
        average: real
        count: integer
    enddictionary

    procedure calculateSumAndAverage(numbers: list of integer) 
        sum &lt;- 0
        count &lt;- length of numbers
        for each number in numbers do
            sum &lt;- sum + number
        endfor
        if count &gt; 0 then
            average &lt;- sum / count
        else
            average &lt;- 0
        endif
    endprocedure

    algorithm
        input numbers
        call calculateSumAndAverage(numbers)
        output sum, average
    endalgorithm

endprogram

